A thunderclap from Hulk would probably push Ant-Man into the sky and maybe daze him, but if not, Hulk would still have an opening to attack. Hulk is one of the most over-powered characters in the Marvel comics, and a big reason why the Thor comics was made was to have someone who could kick Hulk's ass, but I don't think Thor has killed Hulk.
